column5: Happy Birthday Monique.  Very nice insite into your life, thanks for sharing  John

Oh My God Boss...what have you gone and done now ???  It's not safe to leave you on your own...  Happy Birthday Monique...missed meeting you at Lakair last year...maybe this June.  I left early (Friday) and Maureen returned on Saturday.
Happy Birthday Monique !  Hope you have a great one.  Whopper
one more dancer for fun
Hi all,  Just in from Saskatchewon ... just had to check this out.  Happy Birthday Monique!!!!!!!!!!  Love the photos ... good lord TJ ... dunno how you managed it ... lucky bugger.  Pete

Monique have a great day and thanks for sharing the rest of the story I cant wait for the old guys Bday to see his pics but then again can they be any worse then the TUTU?  hope ya had a great one  Mike

Happy Birthday & many more.  Now that brings back some memories... Forgot about the hair... damb alzheimer, one of the side effects of the +40 club. or was that the whisky, shish I forget.  Anyway enjoy  Carl
Happy Birthday Monique!  I know TJ means well LOL
My mother told me once that a man should never mess with a woman because he would never hear the cast lron fry pan.   Happy Birthday
Happy Birthday Monique. Great pics and hope your having a great day.
Happy Birthday Monique,40 is a great year.Are you still coming to Lakair after you have killed TJ?There may be some guys that need a spot in a boat. Joe
Happy B-Day Monique!!!! May you have many more!!!! (TJ won't cuz he's opened up a huge can of whoppass and won't survive the night).
Happy birthday Monique.
TJ .. you are the MAN !  You gotta know Monique will actually love it  .. and If I am wrong ... can I have the boat ?
....Well happy birthday Durl'n. Wish I had time to come up and celebrate with you but I'm sure TJ has other plans?
Best wishes on your birthday Monique!
The greatest of days to you and many many more......
LOL!!!  Happy birthday Monique!
have a good one
OK I think I ask this on everyones behalf... "Sooooo TJ gonna give you the birthday spanks?" and if not someone raise their hand and say I!  LOL  Happy birthday doll-face  Gerritt.

Happy Birthday Monique and you are definitely a beautiful lady.............that guy you are with well he obviously has thought of having suicial tendencies just like he did here.  Go get him girl and please post pics of what you do to him we like seeing him suffer.  Happy Birthday and may you have more happy years to come.  All the best, Sam and Laurie
Happy Birthday Monique I am glad you decided to collect antiques like TJ . Have a good time and break out the cast iron frying pan I think someone needs a good bell ringin.  Art
Happy birthday Monique!  TJ: It was great having you around.  Mike
Happy birthay Monique!  Gee, TJ, I hope I still get to meet you one day!  Stan
Happy birthday Monique, LOL 40 still a kid! Don`t whine, a picture of you with a gun and you still let him get close? You were armed! LOL great pictures! Must have been the disco days?

My one arms broke... and my head is dented but as of midnite... shes fourty.....  May god save us all...  at least till the party on Saturday...  Ill have pictures of that redneck feast also...  Ill string her out as long as im able...  shes had some whiskey.. so she wont be able to hurt me any more till tomorrow....  heres some more.... just to irritate her...        It was nice knowing ya'll

LOL TJ, you never know how that is going to go. My wife had a company put decorations like pink flamingo`s in her sisters yard for her 40th birthday, a normally rational girl. She got twisted, wierd, it`s a number.
Now that it's the "official" day....  HAPPY BIRTHDAY FELLOW BATTER BLIATCH!!
A very happy day to you !!!     Now, when is TJ's birthday.   One good turn deserves another.
HAPPY BIRTHDAY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Great pic  TJ, you realize you're dead now.  Two things I have been led to believe you never talk about a woman -  age and weight.  ps.  Happy Birthday Monique !!
Sweet and innocent,then she met you.LOL  Happy B-Day M.
happy birthday
Please PLEASE tell me that wasn't a wedding picture....
That one caused a tear.L M A O.
Where GCD is from she's almost to old to marry in that picture!   Happy Birthday Monique!
Hey Monique, Happy Biirthday kiddo !!  Here's the way most of us are more used to seeing you though
Oh T.J. you are so "IN TROUBLE"!!!
Too funny...great picture though...just a kid still Monique...Have a great birthday.  Maureen
Hmmmmm, pigtails!  You always were a cutie, weren't you?  Happy Birthday to the Webmistress!
Happy 11th aniversary of your 29th birthday! HH

Ok... i gotta do this quick.. before she catches me... lol...  MODS... dont take her threats seriously...  Roy...  Thats not our wedding picture... lol.. they are below..  Heres some more "early photos"    This is what she looked like on our first date...    Then came our engagement hunt:    We then decided to get married... so we canoed into town:    And let the local preacher tie the old knot in the hotel kitchen!  (Yes ... thats Avery with the curly blonde hair....)    Years later we celebrated her 19th birthday with her first bottle of "Baby Duck"   ... it made her hair all pooofy...    (I GOTTA GO -  SHE'S GONNA FREAK WHEN SHE SEES THIS.....)
Oh to be 40 again! Have a great day Monique. Can't wait to see how you get even TJ, it was nice knowing ya

I'm still trying to figure out what such a cute'y saw in you TJ...but then again I guess pickins are slim in SFalls! LOL  Have a great day Monique...at 40 you're just entering your prime...unlike that lug you're married to.... but then again he still thinks he's 18 so you may very well be fine! LOL
I don't know TJ, but I have a feeling you might be sleepin in the dog house tonight!!   Rob C
I don't know TJ, but I have a feeling you might be sleepin in the dog house tonight!!  Have a Happy Birthday Monique!    Rob C
Well I definately want to see the "after" pictures of TJ from the repercussions of this  Joey
Great photos..get out the body bag. LOL  Roy you crack me up  - wedding picture.

OMG.... T.J. calls me from the truck (cause he's far far away - chicken S##T) and tells me to check out the board. So sorry to expose you all to our life story.  Now everyone knows how we really met. That's OK, his B-Day will come soon!!! Thanks again for the B-Day Wishes.  Gotta go shine the old frying pan so it's ready when hubby gets home

That was an absolutely wonderful glimps into your lives...  It took time for TJ to do that, and in itself, that makes an amazing birthday present...  Happy Birthday Monique, fourty is just the beginning I hear... lol  Enjoy your very special day!  Cheers,  Jen
My older sister told me tears ago that life begins at 40, and when I turned 40 (2 years ago), my life has been so much better. So get ready for life at it's best. Happy Birthday Monique.
Happy B-DAY....   And a dancer for you
Run Forest, RUN!!!!!!!   Monique ~ 40 is the new 20 just with more experiance  Happy Birthday !
Nice thread! All the best to you folks. Oh, and Monique, maybe don't hit him on the head with the fry pan..... he may get even weirder if that's at all possible! LOL!
